&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking to recruit salaried General Practitioners in any one of our Hywel Dda University Health Board managed practices located in Tenby, Kidwelly, Pontyates and Llanelli.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hywel Dda University Health Board operates in a diverse geographical area with high levels of deprivation as well as areas of affluence and growth. The Health Board Managed Practice is situated in the South Pembrokeshire cluster which currently has a registered population of approximately 54,200 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are offering both full and part time positions to work as part of our multidisciplinary teams within our practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Matt McGivern - Business Manager of General Medication &amp; Provider Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;matthew.mcgivern@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
